Package org.ferrumx.core.constant

Enum Class CimQuery

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<CimQuery>
org.ferrumx.core.constant.CimQuery
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<CimQuery>, Constable
public enum CimQuery extends Enum<CimQuery>
Enum representing the predefined WMI (CIM) queries used in the system.

Each constant holds a PowerShell command that queries a specific WMI class and returns the result in JSON format. These queries are typically executed using PowerShell and mapped to corresponding Java objects.
